-> Include ALL categories: RUC, Risk ID, Risk UID, Attrition Provision, Known Attrition, Specific Attrition.
-> NEVER filter out NULL attrition_description.
-> ORDER BY description first, then quarter (Q1->Q2->Q3->Q4).
CORRECT SQL for quarterly breakdown of drivers:
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN "attrition_description" IS NULL OR TRIM("attrition_description") = '' THEN "ruc_risk"
